Description: SynergyMed  is a medical device company that focuses on cancer treatment for human and veterinary applications.
Full Description: SynergyMed Devices is a medical device company focused on the development of cancer tumor treatment products based on an innovative noninvasive ablation technology. The company is registered in the US, based in Boston (with presence in Jerusalem), and is currently at the clinical stage. SynergyMed platform technology may be used as an alternative to surgery for the treatment of early-stage breast, head and neck, skin, and lung cancers for humans and also for the veterinary market. It may also be used for palliative care to relieve pain. The proven technology can locally ablate and destroy cancer tumors, precisely and effectively, without causing any damage to the surrounding healthy tissues. It is based on using specialized electromagnetic applicators which are placed around the region of interest. FDA approved nanoparticles are injected inside the tumor, which absorb the radiated electromagnetic energy efficiently, destroying the tumor without damaging the healthy tissue. The device is controlled through the company’s own developed algorithms which optimize the ablation process while precisely tracking temperature and measuring the administered treatment dose. The company has performed mice studies with breast cancer cell line, showing exceptional results, where the tumor disappeared within only a few days, leaving no scars or traces of cosmetic damage. It has also performed studies on superficial tumors in dogs with excellent results.  SynergyMed Devices Inc. has an experienced team with backgrounds from leading corporate and academic institutions. The company is currently seeking funding and strategic partnerships.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Boston Area, East Coast, New England
Industry Groups: Health Care

Full Description: Oduwa Blockchain Solutions is digital cash open-source software released under the MIT license in 2018 and was inspired by the Pain points of Bitcoin. Oduwacoin is an alternative digital currency to paper money backed by the trustless blockchain technology network. It eliminates human interference, counterfeiting, double spending, and excessive printing like government-issued money. It serves as a medium of exchange, a store of value, and a proof of ownership. Unlike centralized fiat money, Oduwacoin is a decentralized, open-source blockchain-based monetary system. It uses peer-to-peer technology to settle all transactions within its network. Individual coin ownership records are stored in a transparent ledger using cryptography. Oduwa Blockchain Solutions is governed by its native blockchain to secure transaction records, control the creation of additional coins, and verify the transfer of coin ownership.

Description: Software designed for the budding industries of commercial hemp and CBD production and tracking.
Full Description: Hemp has come a long way. It has come out of the shadow of Cannabis to become one of this and next year's hottest industries. While industry has plowed ahead making progress on how to plant, harvest, and process hemp into hundreds of products, what has not progressed is regulation. We believe, and so does everyone else, quite frankly, that when regulations finally show up, many bad habits are going to have been created inside of the industry. What we set out to do was provide good habits. A way to track seed certifications, THC tests, transporations chains of custodies, and proof of origins for the entire industry. This way, when regulations do show up, the right habits are already being practiced, and no lag time for compliance is needed. HempTracker helps track all the necessary documentation to make you legal, and to make your product's origin trackable (example: Nebraska certidfied hemp). It has multiple different log-ins including one for: farmers, processesers/manufacturers, labs, law enforcement, retailers, and buyers.

Description: Motivo Scar Care provides surgical procedure, scare care, and other beauty products and treatments.
Full Description: The Motivo Scar Care® team has found a tremendous need for product improvement within the market. Proper healing is a concern for anyone who has experienced any kind of cut, burn, surgical procedure, traumatic injury, or acne scarring. In addition to the physical effects, we believe that an improved experience will contribute to positive changes in mental health, as those with scars tend to undergo emotional shifts and are more prone to the development of depression and anxiety. Our tagline, "Healing Together," reflects our commitment to fostering a sense of community and inclusion. We believe that when we come together and support each other, we can achieve more than we ever thought possible. Our team is passionate about creating a brand where people of all gender identities, skin types, and backgrounds can feel comfortable and confident in their own skin. We are committed to providing high-quality products that are safe, effective, and affordable, and we believe that everyone deserves to have access to the best scar care available. At Motivo Scar Care®, we want to empower our customers and help them feel confident and comfortable in their skin. We offer a range of products that are designed to help scars heal and fade, and we are dedicated to providing the support and guidance that our customers need to achieve their goals. With our brand, you can trust that you are getting the best possible care for your scars, and that you are part of a supportive and inclusive community. Unlike other scar care brands, we offer products that are suitable for all people and all scar types. Our water-resistant scar tape is a game-changer for anyone who wants to protect their scars while living an active lifestyle. Giving back to communities and causes that are close to our hearts is paramount to Motivo Scar Care®. Not only can consumers and supporters resonate with our brand’s mission, but we are a brand they can stand behind. With every purchase, not only are they healing themselves, but they are helping to heal others in need. Join us on our journey to better scar care, and let's heal together!
